WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:52.300 --> 00:01:54.090
Wh-What?!

3
00:01:54.090 --> 00:01:56.350
King of the Pirates?!

4
00:01:56.350 --> 00:01:59.020
Do you even know what that means?!

5
00:01:59.390 --> 00:02:01.060
I was shocked, too!

6
00:02:01.060 --> 00:02:02.770
But Luffy is serious!

7
00:02:02.770 --> 00:02:04.310
That's how he is!

8
00:02:07.570 --> 00:02:13.280
The First

9
00:02:08.110 --> 00:02:09.690
Here! I got your treasure back!

10
00:02:09.690 --> 00:02:13.280
Is it one of these? I couldn't tell,
so I brought all three.

11
00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:15.240
All three are mine.

12
00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:18.120
I use a three-sword style.

13
00:02:18.120 --> 00:02:22.620
If we fight together now,
the government will see you as a bad guy.

14
00:02:22.620 --> 00:02:26.000
Either that, or stay
and let the Marines kill you.

15
00:02:26.630 --> 00:02:28.630
Are you some kind of demon spawn?

16
00:02:28.630 --> 00:02:31.510
But hey, if my only other option is death,

17
00:02:31.510 --> 00:02:34.800
then you've got yourself a pirate!

18
00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:38.180
Awesome! So you'll join my crew?!

19
00:02:38.430 --> 00:02:40.930
Alright! Woo-hoo! This is perfect!

20
00:02:40.930 --> 00:02:44.020
Great! Now untie these
stupid ropes already!

21
00:02:41.810 --> 00:02:44.020
Alright!

22
00:02:44.020 --> 00:02:45.770
What is he?

23
00:02:45.770 --> 00:02:47.810
He bounced the bullets back!

24
00:02:48.190 --> 00:02:50.940
That straw hat man is
no ordinary human.

25
00:02:50.940 --> 00:02:54.570
He must have eaten one of
those rumored devil fruits!

26
00:02:54.570 --> 00:02:55.570
A devil fruit?!

27
00:02:55.570 --> 00:02:57.280
The secret treasures of the sea?!

28
00:02:57.280 --> 00:02:58.950
Hurry! Hurry!

29
00:02:58.950 --> 00:03:02.750
Damn! These knots are tight!

30
00:03:01.290 --> 00:03:02.750
Hey! Quit screwing around!

31
00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:07.250
I don't care who they are,
all who oppose me will be executed!

32
00:03:07.250 --> 00:03:09.710
If guns won't work, gut them!

33
00:03:14.090 --> 00:03:16.590
Huh, that's weird! It got
tighter for some reason!

34
00:03:16.590 --> 00:03:18.300
Dammit! Swords! Now!

35
00:03:21.470 --> 00:03:22.600
Luffy!

36
00:03:31.770 --> 00:03:33.860
Roronoa Zoro!

37
00:03:35.150 --> 00:03:36.490
So cool!

38
00:03:38.200 --> 00:03:39.870
Move and you're dead.

39
00:03:40.780 --> 00:03:42.660
He's too scary!

40
00:03:46.660 --> 00:03:49.080
I'll be a pirate. I promise you that.

41
00:03:49.790 --> 00:03:53.590
Now that I've fought the Marines,
I'm officially an outlaw.

42
00:03:53.590 --> 00:03:56.220
But let's get one thing straight.

43
00:03:56.220 --> 00:03:58.800
I'm only doing this
to accomplish my dream.

44
00:03:58.800 --> 00:03:59.590
Dream?

45
00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:02.560
To be the world's
greatest swordsman!

46
00:04:03.350 --> 00:04:06.480
So if you ever make me
abandon my dream,

47
00:04:06.480 --> 00:04:10.610
you'll need to commit harakiri
to earn my forgiveness!

48
00:04:10.610 --> 00:04:12.860
The world's greatest swordsman?

49
00:04:12.860 --> 00:04:14.360
I like it!

50
00:04:14.360 --> 00:04:18.070
That's exactly who the Pirate King
needs on his crew!

51
00:04:18.820 --> 00:04:20.200
You sure talk big.

52
00:04:20.200 --> 00:04:23.080
At this point, even if I'm
a criminal or whatever,

53
00:04:23.080 --> 00:04:25.700
the world's gonna know my name!

54
00:04:25.950 --> 00:04:28.210
What are you standing around for?!

55
00:04:28.210 --> 00:04:30.250
Slaughter them this instant!

56
00:04:31.670 --> 00:04:33.250
Zoro, duck!

57
00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:38.010
Gum-Gum Whip!

58
00:04:40.640 --> 00:04:43.260
Y-You did it! Incredible!

59
00:04:43.260 --> 00:04:45.010
What the hell are you?

60
00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:47.980
I ate the Gum-Gum Fruit.

61
00:04:48.230 --> 00:04:49.690
Gum-Gum Fruit?

62
00:04:49.690 --> 00:04:51.400
He's a rubber man!

63
00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:53.900
So he does have devil fruit powers!

64
00:04:53.900 --> 00:04:56.400
Captain! We don't
stand a chance against them!

65
00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:58.030
These guys are too much!

66
00:04:58.030 --> 00:05:00.110
We can't even
handle Zoro by himself!

67
00:05:02.820 --> 00:05:04.580
This is a direct order!

68
00:05:04.580 --> 00:05:08.330
Every weakling whining just now
must shoot himself in the head!

69
00:05:08.330 --> 00:05:11.620
I won't tolerate cowardice
among my men!

70
00:05:14.040 --> 00:05:16.880
These troops are deranged!

71
00:05:17.460 --> 00:05:18.760
Luffy!

72
00:05:20.630 --> 00:05:23.340
Let those Marines have it!

73
00:05:32.270 --> 00:05:36.900
Scum without rank or status
have no right to oppose me!

74
00:05:36.900 --> 00:05:40.780
I am Captain Axe-Hand
Morgan of the Marines!

75
00:05:40.780 --> 00:05:42.530
I'm Luffy!

76
00:05:42.530 --> 00:05:43.410
Nice to meet you!

77
00:05:43.780 --> 00:05:45.910
Die!

78
00:05:55.130 --> 00:05:56.670
Th-The captain!

79
00:05:56.670 --> 00:05:59.340
Y-You puny...

80
00:06:01.170 --> 00:06:03.180
Die!

81
00:06:03.180 --> 00:06:04.470
No thanks!

82
00:06:07.180 --> 00:06:09.180
C-Captain Morgan is...

83
00:06:11.560 --> 00:06:12.890
He's getting thrashed!

84
00:06:14.730 --> 00:06:18.940
You call yourself a Marine?!
You're ruining Koby's dream!

85
00:06:20.030 --> 00:06:22.190
Hold it, straw hat guy!

86
00:06:22.190 --> 00:06:23.360
Look over here!

87
00:06:25.280 --> 00:06:27.620
I said hold it! Are you stupid?!

88
00:06:27.620 --> 00:06:30.750
Pay attention! I have a hostage here!

89
00:06:30.750 --> 00:06:32.580
Master Helmeppo!

90
00:06:32.580 --> 00:06:33.750
Hey.

91
00:06:35.710 --> 00:06:38.710
Don't move if you value this guy's life!

92
00:06:38.710 --> 00:06:41.920
One move and I'll shoot!

93
00:06:45.760 --> 00:06:47.140
Luffy!

94
00:06:47.140 --> 00:06:50.850
Don't stop on my account!
Even if it means he kills me!

95
00:06:51.270 --> 00:06:53.270
Yeah, I know!

96
00:06:53.270 --> 00:06:55.140
It's no use, you idiot son!

97
00:06:55.140 --> 00:06:57.770
Koby really is ready to die!

98
00:06:58.900 --> 00:07:00.020
Don't move!

99
00:07:00.020 --> 00:07:02.610
I told you not to move! I-I'll shoot!

100
00:07:03.490 --> 00:07:05.200
B-Behind you!

101
00:07:05.200 --> 00:07:06.530
Gum-Gum...

102
00:07:06.530 --> 00:07:11.040
I am Captain Axe-Hand
Morgan of the Marines!

103
00:07:12.330 --> 00:07:14.290
Daddy! Kill him, quick!

104
00:07:13.580 --> 00:07:15.410
Pistol!

105
00:07:19.960 --> 00:07:21.380
Nice!

106
00:07:30.510 --> 00:07:31.350
Zoro.

107
00:07:31.850 --> 00:07:35.020
It was my pleasure, Captain.

108
00:07:42.190 --> 00:07:43.610
Captain Morgan lost!

109
00:07:43.610 --> 00:07:44.740
Unbelievable!

110
00:07:44.740 --> 00:07:45.860
These guys are insane!

111
00:07:47.610 --> 00:07:51.580
If any of you still wanna
try your luck, bring it on!

112
00:07:55.660 --> 00:07:57.710
Hooray! Hooray!

113
00:07:56.660 --> 00:07:57.710
We're free!

114
00:07:57.710 --> 00:07:58.830
Yahoo!

115
00:07:58.830 --> 00:08:00.500
Morgan's reign is over!

116
00:08:00.500 --> 00:08:02.670
Hooray for the Marines!

117
00:08:02.920 --> 00:08:03.670
What gives?

118
00:08:03.670 --> 00:08:06.920
Why are they so happy
that we beat their captain?

119
00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:10.140
Everyone was just afraid of Morgan!

120
00:08:14.430 --> 00:08:16.060
What's wrong, Zoro?!

121
00:08:16.060 --> 00:08:17.180
Are you hurt?!

122
00:08:17.940 --> 00:08:18.890
I'm...

123
00:08:18.890 --> 00:08:20.400
hungry...

124
00:08:25.820 --> 00:08:27.360
I'm stuffed!

125
00:08:27.700 --> 00:08:32.320
Three weeks with no food put me
in worse shape than I thought!

126
00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:38.540
Huh? You're finished already?

127
00:08:39.040 --> 00:08:42.250
How the hell do you have
a bigger appetite than me?!

128
00:08:42.250 --> 00:08:44.800
It tastes good! Right, Koby?

129
00:08:44.800 --> 00:08:47.760
It's awfully kind of you
to treat me as well.

130
00:08:48.010 --> 00:08:51.220
It's no trouble! You saved
our town, after all!

131
00:08:51.470 --> 00:08:53.850
You're really great, mister!

132
00:08:53.850 --> 00:08:57.220
Yeah, I am! And I'm
gonna be even greater!

133
00:08:57.220 --> 00:09:00.020
After all, I'm gonna be
King of the Pirates!

134
00:09:00.310 --> 00:09:02.100
And now I've got a crew!

135
00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:06.690
Hey, tell me! Where are
you guys gonna go now?

136
00:09:06.690 --> 00:09:09.950
Isn't it obvious?! The Grand Line!

137
00:09:11.530 --> 00:09:13.660
There are only two of you!

138
00:09:13.660 --> 00:09:16.580
There's no way you can go there!
No way! No way! No way!

139
00:09:16.830 --> 00:09:20.290
Is the Grand Line that bad of a place?

140
00:09:20.290 --> 00:09:22.290
You bet it is!

141
00:09:22.290 --> 00:09:26.630
You know this world
has two oceans, right?

142
00:09:26.630 --> 00:09:31.300
And how there's a giant landmass
called the Red Line separating them?

143
00:09:31.300 --> 00:09:34.470
Supposedly, a city lies smack dab
in the middle of the Red Line,

144
00:09:34.470 --> 00:09:39.060
and the Grand Line intersects
this city at a right angle,

145
00:09:39.060 --> 00:09:42.020
stretching all the way
around the world.

146
00:09:42.560 --> 00:09:48.570
They say that Pirate King Gold Roger
obtained everything this world had to offer.

147
00:09:48.570 --> 00:09:55.450
And he left the great treasure
One Piece there, in the Grand Line.

148
00:09:55.450 --> 00:09:59.290
Now pirates from all over
set sail for that sea!

149
00:09:59.290 --> 00:10:04.960
It's become a fierce battlefield.
People call it the Pirate Graveyard!

150
00:10:09.300 --> 00:10:15.890
I've had patrons tell me that nobody
returns from the Grand Line alive.

151
00:10:16.140 --> 00:10:21.100
But the One Piece has gotta
be there, so we're going!

152
00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:23.060
Well, guess that's that!

153
00:10:23.060 --> 00:10:25.100
Zoro! Even you?!

154
00:10:25.100 --> 00:10:26.940
You're not going, so what's the issue?

155
00:10:26.940 --> 00:10:30.070
I-It's because I'm worried about you!

156
00:10:30.070 --> 00:10:31.740
Is that so wrong?!

157
00:10:31.740 --> 00:10:36.490
I realize Luffy and I haven't known
each other long, but we're friends!

158
00:10:36.490 --> 00:10:37.450
Am I right?

159
00:10:37.830 --> 00:10:41.410
Yeah! Even if we're apart,
we'll always be friends!

160
00:10:45.330 --> 00:10:49.210
Since I was a little kid,
I could never make friends...

161
00:10:49.210 --> 00:10:52.840
much less find anyone
willing to fight for my sake...

162
00:10:52.840 --> 00:10:56.930
I mean, really, I've never truly fought for anything.

163
00:10:58.800 --> 00:11:04.060
But you two taught me
how to live by my beliefs!

164
00:11:04.060 --> 00:11:07.520
I've decided to make
my childhood dream a reality!

165
00:11:07.520 --> 00:11:09.400
I want to join the Marines!

166
00:11:09.400 --> 00:11:12.610
Shouldn't you be more
worried about yourself, then?

167
00:11:13.240 --> 00:11:13.820
What...?

168
00:11:14.490 --> 00:11:15.740
Cabin boy or no,

169
00:11:15.740 --> 00:11:19.530
you did spend two years
on Alvida's pirate ship.

170
00:11:21.830 --> 00:11:24.500
Marine intelligence
is nothing to scoff at.

171
00:11:24.500 --> 00:11:27.290
If they learn about your past,
they won't let you enlist.

172
00:11:27.960 --> 00:11:29.840
N-Now that you mention it...

173
00:11:30.880 --> 00:11:32.000
Pardon me!

174
00:11:36.340 --> 00:11:39.300
Is it true that you are pirates?!

175
00:11:39.550 --> 00:11:44.560
Yeah! I got my first member,
so we're officially a pirate crew now!

176
00:11:44.810 --> 00:11:50.440
We appreciate that you saved our
base and this town from that tyrant!

177
00:11:50.440 --> 00:11:53.280
However, after confirming
you are indeed pirates,

178
00:11:53.280 --> 00:11:56.070
in the name of the Marines,
we cannot stand idly by!

179
00:11:56.950 --> 00:11:59.820
You will leave this town at once!

180
00:11:59.820 --> 00:12:03.580
To show our gratitude, we won't
report you to headquarters.

181
00:12:03.580 --> 00:12:04.540
Hey, Marines!

182
00:12:05.040 --> 00:12:06.580
What the hell are you saying?!

183
00:12:06.580 --> 00:12:10.290
Even you guys were terrified
of Morgan's iron rule!

184
00:12:10.290 --> 00:12:13.500
We owe these people our lives!

185
00:12:13.500 --> 00:12:15.090
– Yeah! Yeah!
– Uh-huh! That's right!

186
00:12:18.590 --> 00:12:20.010
Welp, time to go!

187
00:12:20.590 --> 00:12:22.100
Thanks for the food, lady!

188
00:12:22.390 --> 00:12:25.020
You guys are leaving already?

189
00:12:25.310 --> 00:12:26.390
Yep.

190
00:12:33.820 --> 00:12:35.690
Aren't you part of their crew?

191
00:12:35.690 --> 00:12:37.650
Huh? I...

192
00:12:37.650 --> 00:12:38.950
I'm...

193
00:12:43.330 --> 00:12:44.160
Hold it!

194
00:12:44.410 --> 00:12:46.160
Well? Is he?!

195
00:12:46.950 --> 00:12:50.170
Wanna know what
this guy's been up to?

196
00:12:51.170 --> 00:12:52.920
Luffy! You wouldn't!

197
00:12:53.250 --> 00:12:56.380
There was this really,
really fat pirate lady,

198
00:12:56.380 --> 00:12:58.130
I think her name was Ahilda.

199
00:12:58.130 --> 00:13:00.130
Luffy!

200
00:13:00.680 --> 00:13:02.800
If they find out I was
on a pirate ship,

201
00:13:02.800 --> 00:13:05.390
I'll never get to join the Marines!

202
00:13:05.390 --> 00:13:07.390
And she had this iron club.

203
00:13:07.390 --> 00:13:10.020
Man, she was an ugly hag!

204
00:13:10.940 --> 00:13:14.440
And for two whole years,
this guy was her...

205
00:13:15.070 --> 00:13:19.650
Please don't! Please don't, Luffy!

206
00:13:19.650 --> 00:13:20.860
Shut up!

207
00:13:28.160 --> 00:13:29.790
Now you've done it, you bastard!

208
00:13:30.370 --> 00:13:35.250
You jerk! Take that!
And that! And this!

209
00:13:35.500 --> 00:13:36.880
Stop that!

210
00:13:36.880 --> 00:13:40.470
There's already been enough
trouble in this town as it is!

211
00:13:40.880 --> 00:13:41.430
Hey!

212
00:13:41.800 --> 00:13:43.340
You're going too far.

213
00:13:43.340 --> 00:13:44.850
That's enough.

214
00:13:49.770 --> 00:13:52.520
It's clear that you guys
aren't crewmates!

215
00:13:52.520 --> 00:13:55.020
Now, leave this town immediately!

216
00:14:00.940 --> 00:14:02.240
He...

217
00:14:04.200 --> 00:14:06.280
He did that on purpose...

218
00:14:10.160 --> 00:14:12.210
For me...

219
00:14:12.710 --> 00:14:15.960
He purposely got me riled up
to make me hit him.

220
00:14:17.670 --> 00:14:22.630
Even in the very end,
I wound up relying on him!

221
00:14:25.890 --> 00:14:28.850
Nothing's changed at all!

222
00:14:31.270 --> 00:14:33.560
Am I that dense?!

223
00:14:34.060 --> 00:14:35.270
Please!

224
00:14:36.110 --> 00:14:38.940
Please... let me join the Marines!

225
00:14:38.940 --> 00:14:42.070
I'll gladly be a cabin boy
or whatever else...

226
00:14:42.070 --> 00:14:44.490
if it means I can be a Marine!

227
00:14:47.740 --> 00:14:48.740
Commander!

228
00:14:48.740 --> 00:14:50.450
I'm against the idea!

229
00:14:51.370 --> 00:14:54.000
I still don't fully trust this kid!

230
00:14:54.000 --> 00:14:57.080
There are reports of pirates
planting spies in the Marines.

231
00:14:57.580 --> 00:15:00.090
We'll need to conduct
a background check first–

232
00:15:00.550 --> 00:15:04.090
The man you see before you
will become a Marine officer!

233
00:15:11.140 --> 00:15:14.270
Countless comrades of ours
have been killed by pirates.

234
00:15:14.270 --> 00:15:15.940
Don't take the Marines lightly.

235
00:15:17.190 --> 00:15:17.900
Then...

236
00:15:18.270 --> 00:15:20.150
Permission to join, granted!

237
00:15:22.320 --> 00:15:23.150
Yes, sir!

238
00:15:24.780 --> 00:15:27.110
Your acting was horrible.

239
00:15:27.110 --> 00:15:28.870
I bet they saw right through it.

240
00:15:29.450 --> 00:15:32.910
It's all up to Koby now.
I know he's got this.

241
00:15:32.910 --> 00:15:34.660
Well, it's a good way to leave.

242
00:15:34.660 --> 00:15:36.870
Heading out with
everyone mad at you...

243
00:15:37.120 --> 00:15:38.630
How pirate-like!

244
00:15:40.090 --> 00:15:41.130
That's true!

245
00:15:41.130 --> 00:15:42.550
Luffy!

246
00:15:41.880 --> 00:15:42.550
Huh?

247
00:15:44.550 --> 00:15:48.890
Thank you! I'll never forget
all you've done for me!

248
00:15:49.680 --> 00:15:53.270
First time I've heard of
a Marine thanking a pirate.

249
00:15:56.390 --> 00:15:58.850
We'll meet again, Koby!

250
00:15:59.350 --> 00:16:00.110
Luffy...

251
00:16:00.110 --> 00:16:02.320
Bye!

252
00:16:02.570 --> 00:16:05.030
At-ten-tion!

253
00:16:07.990 --> 00:16:10.950
See ya!

254
00:16:11.740 --> 00:16:13.910
That's a great friend
you have there.

255
00:16:18.830 --> 00:16:19.960
Yes, sir!

256
00:16:21.170 --> 00:16:25.800
Marine regulations prohibit
the saluting of pirates!

257
00:16:25.800 --> 00:16:28.680
As punishment,
no rations for three days!

258
00:16:28.680 --> 00:16:29.680
Understood?!

259
00:16:29.680 --> 00:16:30.720
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

260
00:16:33.810 --> 00:16:36.350
Alright! Let's go!

261
00:16:36.350 --> 00:16:40.770
Set sail for the Grand Line!
